Purify Blood

This spell is one of a druid's limited number of
healing rituals.  It acts to purge poisons from
the target's bloodstream, preventing them from
doing any further damage.  At higher levels of
mastery, it also has influence over alcohol in
the bloodstream.

Command: purify <target> (defaults to caster)
Base Cost: 35
Base Recovery: short
Base Effect: heal (poisons), detox
Base Duration: instant
Guild Level: 11
